Package it.polimi.ingsw.parsers

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GsonParser
    A parser to analyze and manage Json string representing classes.
    SetupParser
    Public class used to read parameters from a specific xml file that contains: - the ip address to which the client must connect if the value entered by the user is wrong
    ToolCardParser
    Public class used to read from a specific xml file the parameters of the 12 tool cards to use during the game.
    WindowParser
    Public class used that receives as input the name of a specific window and read its parameters from a xml file.
